title: Experimental Music Compilation (Alternative, weird, bizarre)
description:
Tired of the mainstream music? Want to challenge yourself with some really experimental and groundbreaking music?

This torrent is meant for you to get an insight in the most insane, alrernative and experimenting artists out there. I hope that this can be an ear opener for you.

Remember to support these artists if you like them, and support the copy-left ideology. Piracy is not stealing. Piracy is sharing.
